high_descs: Turn left and move forward to the middle of the counter between the refrigerator and the oven and then turn right and move up to the counter.
Take the tomato from the rear corner of the counter closest to the stove.
Turn around and move to the sink next to the coffee maker.
Place the tomato in the sink and wash it with water. Turn off the faucet and pick up the tomato from the sink.
Move slightly to the left and then look up at the microwave above the sink.
Place the tomato on the plate in the microwave and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the counter.
Pick up a tomato from the counter.
Walk across the room to the sink.
Clean the tomato in the sink.
Turn to your left and walk towards the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the left of the stove
Grab the tomato on the counter
Turn around, walk to the sink
Put the tomato in the sink, open the faucet, wash the tomato and turn off the faucet, take the tomato
Walk to the left a little to the microwave
Open the microwave, put the tomato in, close the microwave
anns.task_desc: Wash the tomato, put the tomato in the microwave
